snippet.title: Creepiest Pictures On the Internet - 2

localized.description:
WARNING: Some of these images might shock and disturb viewers of a sensitive disposition due to their graphic nature. 
This is a collection of the creepiest pictures and animated gifs on the web. 
Not all of the pictures are paranormal in nature, some are just uncanny images that have an inexplicably eerie feel to them. 
Don't have nightmares!

Part 1- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZrdXHJjlSQk&list=PLiP5xR323QzjSPxdbWgqMMewEb8nNPa23&index=2
